WEBVTT

00:04:28.339 --> 00:04:30.934
scary, a bit much?

00:04:30.958 --> 00:04:36.529
But the image of young boys
screaming their lungs out for a footballer

00:04:36.553 --> 00:04:37.887
is perfectly normal?

00:04:38.919 --> 00:04:40.653
Boys crying at the footie,

00:04:40.677 --> 00:04:42.544
that's the love of the game.

00:04:42.903 --> 00:04:45.569
Girls crying at a Justin Bieber concert?

00:04:45.981 --> 00:04:47.131
That's pathetic.

00:04:47.895 --> 00:04:50.315
And as soon as I realized
this double standard,

00:04:50.339 --> 00:04:53.022
I realized that all
of my curiosity about fangirls

00:04:53.046 --> 00:04:55.776
had been sparked
by exactly the same judgments.

00:04:55.800 --> 00:04:59.098
I, too, had suspected
that they were a bit crazy.

00:04:59.624 --> 00:05:02.523
I'd looked at images
of girls screaming for the Beatles,